Kenapa tak terpikirkan olehku?

1143
01:20:42,840 --> 01:20:44,365
<i>Berapa lama lagi ia tiba?</i>

1144
01:20:44,520 --> 01:20:46,522
<i>- Lima menit.</i>
- Baik.

1145
01:20:46,880 --> 01:20:48,564
Johnny, awasi monitor-monitor ini.

1146
01:20:48,720 --> 01:20:50,006
Apa yang terjadi?

1147
